It just seems that each time you have posted and addressed me in one form or another you have gone back to the past and seem to blame me or others that are now posting for the absence of those that used to post but are no longer doing so. Spatz does the same thing. E-mail them to find out. Take a survey and find out why they haven’t return. You might be surprise, by what you’ll find out, that it just may not have anything to do with the POV site.<br><br>
